3) move xtime_lock into ktimed
4) move wall_to_monotonic into ktimed
5) move calc_load.count into ktimed
6) move avenrun into ktimed.
7) patches to use ktimed.jiffies64 on various arches (with the problem of 
aliasing jiffies)
